  "body": "###### Info\r\n\r\n- **Version**: MyEtherWallet v6.5.5\r\n- **Browser**: Chrome\r\n- **OS**: Windows\r\n- **Page Url**: https://myetherwallet.com/wallet/dashboard\r\n- **Network**: XDC Network (Mainnet)\r\n\r\n###### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Access the wallet with Browser Extension(XDCPay Version 6.2.10)\r\n2. Select XDC Network (Mainnet)\r\n3. On Dashboard, Add any XRC20 token by clicking on \"Add Token\" from the \"Custom Tokens\" dropdown.\r\n4. Once the token is added successfully with minimum balance, click on the \"Send XDC\" button.\r\n5. Select the XRC20 token from the \"Token\" dropdown, enter the amount, and XRC20 address with the 0x prefix.\r\n6. To initiate the transaction, the \"Next\" button is not getting enabled to process further.\r\n\r\n\r\n###### What do you expect to happen?\r\nXRC20 Token transactions should work smoothly.\r\n\r\n###### What happens instead?\r\nXRC20 Token transactions are not working.\r\n\r\n###### Screenshot\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/39384359/171588286-7c5a1be5-01a0-46fd-886d-b177b46cd66f.png)\r\n",
